QuestData.Title: Seavine: Fisherman Tinnak's Gift
QuestData.Description: <You can see the poor fisherman's spectral hand is still gripping a thread woven of a very strong, yet light, kelp. Nunvuq in Iskaara might find a use for that.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the seavine tope to Nunvuq in Iskaara.
